sense.def:
To complain about something
pomeni povedati, da z nečim nismo zadovoljni.

seg.quote: People had complained to Uncle Harold about his fights.
‘He never told me, sir,’ Watson complained.
She complained that the office was not ‘businesslike’.

sense.def:
To complain of pain or illness
pomeni povedati, da nas nekaj boli ali da smo bolni.

seg.quote: He complained of pain in the chest.
